      },
      "date": "2017-12-04 07:14:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Andreas, yes, this is not necessary for migration, originally this was added because in migration implementation, the migrating dir will contain both source and target stripes, but it doesn't really add source stripes, but just adds them in its lmm. I'll get rid of this later with new implementation.",
