        "subject": "LU-4684 lod: store dir stripe fids in lmm",
        "message": "LU-4684 lod: store dir stripe fids in lmm\n\nTo support directory migration, directory stripe fids should be stored\nin lmm. To adapt to this change, lfsck code should read lmm into a\nbuf.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5e5ed421a5f4fc2225a3dc18e1ed9bc3f2652af9\n"
